title: National Parks of New York Harbor: Traveling Trunks
body: Traveling Trunks         This traveling trunk includes eight "explorations" that combine science with art and music. It is available to teachers of Staten Island schools, please call 718-354-4530 x 237. NPS PHOTO  Both Statue of Liberty - Ellis Island and Gateway National Recreation Area have traveling trunks. Contact the parks for more information. Statue of Liberty- Ellis Island Gateway National Recreation Area
